═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

A.D.H.D | A D Hway Design
Destiny Holloway, Cleveland, OH
hello@adhwaydesign.com

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

INVOICE #: ${num || 'TBD'}
DATE: ${date || new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
DUE DATE: Upon receipt

BILL TO:
${name}
${biz}

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

DESCRIPTION                                           AMOUNT
${desc}                                    $${amount}

